  "detailed_description": "<strong>Arkos 2</strong> is a first-person fantasy shooter with destructible voxel environment. You play the old wizard Arkos, who has to save the land of the twilight<br>Game inspired by the classic old first person shooters of the 90s like <strong>Heretic</strong>, <strong>Hexen</strong> and <strong>Catacomb3D</strong>, but powered with some bloody Voxels!<br><br>The ancient evil is back!<br><br>Next Generation of Voxel Engine with Destructible voxel environment<br>Five Episodes with a Boss Battles<br>Classic style MIDI Soundtrack<br>3 Difficulty Modes<br>5 Unique Weapons<br>Pure retro action with some puzzle elements",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Arkos 2</strong> is a first-person fantasy shooter with destructible voxel environment. You play the old wizard Arkos, who has to save the land of the twilight<br>Game inspired by the classic old first person shooters of the 90s like <strong>Heretic</strong>, <strong>Hexen</strong> and <strong>Catacomb3D</strong>, but powered with some bloody Voxels!<br><br>The ancient evil is back!<br><br>Next Generation of Voxel Engine with Destructible voxel environment<br>Five Episodes with a Boss Battles<br>Classic style MIDI Soundtrack<br>3 Difficulty Modes<br>5 Unique Weapons<br>Pure retro action with some puzzle elements",
